sequenceDiagram
    participant CB as Customer Browser
    participant MS as Merchant Server
    participant PG as Payment Gateway
    participant TDS as 3DS Server
    participant DS as Directory Server<br/>(Visa/MC)
    participant ACS as ACS<br/>(Issuing Bank)

    Note over CB,ACS: 🔒 3D Secure 2.0 Authentication Flow

    CB->>MS: Submit payment (card details tokenized)
    MS->>PG: Create payment intent
    PG->>TDS: Initiate 3DS authentication

    Note over TDS,DS: Version Negotiation
    TDS->>DS: AReq (Authentication Request)<br/>with device fingerprint data
    DS->>ACS: Forward AReq to issuer ACS
    
    Note over ACS: Risk-Based Analysis:<br/>• Device fingerprint<br/>• Transaction history<br/>• Amount & merchant risk<br/>• Cardholder behavior

    alt Frictionless Flow (Low Risk)
        ACS->>DS: ARes - Frictionless authenticated ✅
        DS->>TDS: Forward ARes
        TDS->>PG: Authentication successful<br/>ECI = 05 (Visa) / 02 (MC)
        PG->>MS: 3DS complete - proceed to authorize
        MS->>CB: ✅ Payment processing (no challenge shown)
    else Challenge Flow (Higher Risk)
        ACS->>DS: ARes - Challenge required ⚠️
        DS->>TDS: Forward ARes with challenge URL
        TDS->>PG: Challenge required
        PG->>MS: Return challenge data
        MS->>CB: Display challenge iframe

        Note over CB,ACS: Customer Authentication Challenge
        CB->>ACS: Render challenge (OTP / Biometric / Password)
        
        alt Challenge Succeeded
            ACS->>CB: Challenge completed ✅
            ACS->>DS: RReq (Result Request) - Authenticated
            DS->>TDS: Forward authentication result
            TDS->>PG: Authentication successful<br/>ECI = 05 (Visa) / 02 (MC)
            PG->>MS: 3DS complete - proceed
            MS->>CB: ✅ Payment authorized
        else Challenge Failed
            ACS->>CB: Challenge failed ❌
            ACS->>DS: RReq - Not authenticated
            DS->>TDS: Forward failure result
            TDS->>PG: Authentication failed<br/>ECI = 07 (Visa) / 00 (MC)
            PG->>MS: 3DS failed
            MS->>CB: ❌ Payment declined
        else Challenge Timeout
            Note over CB: Customer abandons challenge
            ACS->>DS: RReq - Timeout
            DS->>TDS: Forward timeout
            TDS->>PG: Authentication timeout
            PG->>MS: 3DS timed out
            MS->>CB: ⚠️ Payment expired - try again
        end
    else Attempt (Issuer not enrolled)
        ACS->>DS: ARes - Issuer not participating
        DS->>TDS: Forward ARes
        TDS->>PG: Attempted authentication<br/>ECI = 06 (Visa) / 01 (MC)
        PG->>MS: Proceed with liability shift to issuer
        MS->>CB: ✅ Payment processing
    end

    Note over CB,ACS: Liability Shift: With successful 3DS,<br/>fraud liability shifts from merchant to issuer
